CakePHP User Plugin

A CakePHP Plugin for User authentication management

INSTALLATION
------------

1. Copy User to your app/Plugin directory
2. Load the plugin in app/Config/bootstrap.php

CONFIGURATION
---------------

TODO: Make configurable

USAGE
---------------

Access the plugin at /user/users/login

